<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(25, 47, 96); font-family: &quot;Noto Sans USAese&quot;, &quot;ヒラギノ角ゴ Pro W3&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro&quot;, メイリオ, Meiryo, Osaka, &quot;ＭＳ Ｐゴシック&quot;, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">(3) When it is particularly necessary to improve public health or promote the sound development of children and it is difficult to obtain the consent of the individual</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(25, 47, 96); font-family: &quot;Noto Sans USAese&quot;, &quot;ヒラギノ角ゴ Pro W3&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro&quot;, メイリオ, Meiryo, Osaka, &quot;ＭＳ Ｐゴシック&quot;, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">(4) When it is necessary for a national institution, a local public entity, or a person entrusted with it to cooperate in performing the duties stipulated by laws and regulations, and with the consent of the individual, the performance of such duties When it may interfere with</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(25, 47, 96); font-family: &quot;Noto Sans USAese&quot;, &quot;ヒラギノ角ゴ Pro W3&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro&quot;, メイリオ, Meiryo, Osaka, &quot;ＭＳ Ｐゴシック&quot;, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">4-3 When we provide personal data to a third party, we create and store records in accordance with Article 25 of the Personal Information Protection Law.</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(25, 47, 96); font-family: &quot;Noto Sans USAese&quot;, &quot;ヒラギノ角ゴ Pro W3&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro&quot;, メイリオ, Meiryo, Osaka, &quot;ＭＳ Ｐゴシック&quot;, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">4-4 When receiving personal data from a third party, the Company shall make necessary confirmations in accordance with Article 26 of the Personal Information Protection Law, and shall create and save records relating to such confirmations.</p>
<h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Noto Sans USAese&quot;, &quot;ヒラギノ角ゴ Pro W3&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro&quot;, メイリオ, Meiryo, Osaka, &quot;ＭＳ Ｐゴシック&quot;, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, verdana, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 32px; color: rgb(25, 47, 96); margin: 40px 0px 15px; font-size: 26px; padding: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">5. Disclosure of personal information</h3>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(25, 47, 96); font-family: &quot;Noto Sans USAese&quot;, &quot;ヒラギノ角ゴ Pro W3&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro&quot;, メイリオ, Meiryo, Osaka, &quot;ＭＳ Ｐゴシック&quot;, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">When the user requests disclosure of personal information based on the provisions of the Personal Information Protection Law, the Company confirms that it is a request from the user himself and discloses it to the user without delay (If the personal information does not exist, we will notify you.)&nbsp;However, this does not apply if the Company has no obligation to disclose under the Personal Information Protection Law and other laws and regulations.&nbsp;Please note that there is a fee (1,000 yen per case) for disclosure of personal information.</p>
<h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Noto Sans USAese&quot;, &quot;ヒラギノ角ゴ Pro W3&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro&quot;, メイリオ, Meiryo, Osaka, &quot;ＭＳ Ｐゴシック&quot;, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, verdana, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 32px; color: rgb(25, 47, 96); margin: 40px 0px 15px; font-size: 26px; padding: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">6. Correction of personal information and suspension of use</h3>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(25, 47, 96); font-family: &quot;Noto Sans USAese&quot;, &quot;ヒラギノ角ゴ Pro W3&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro&quot;, メイリオ, Meiryo, Osaka, &quot;ＭＳ Ｐゴシック&quot;, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">6-1 The Company, if the user requests (1) correction of the contents based on the provisions of the Personal Information Protection Law for the reason that the personal information is not true, and (2) the scope of the purpose of use announced in advance If you are requested to suspend the use of the data in accordance with the Personal Information Protection Law for the reason that it has been handled in excess of After confirming that the request has been made, we will conduct the necessary investigation without delay, and based on the result, correct or suspend the use of the personal information and notify the user accordingly.&nbsp;If we decide not to correct or suspend the use for reasonable reasons, we will notify the user to that effect.</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(25, 47, 96); font-family: &quot;Noto Sans USAese&quot;, &quot;ヒラギノ角ゴ Pro W3&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro&quot;, メイリオ, Meiryo, Osaka, &quot;ＭＳ Ｐゴシック&quot;, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">6-2 If the user requests that the user's personal information be erased, and if the Company determines that it is necessary to respond to the request, the Company will confirm that the request is from the user himself Deletes the personal information and informs the user accordingly.</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(25, 47, 96); font-family: &quot;Noto Sans USAese&quot;, &quot;ヒラギノ角ゴ Pro W3&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro&quot;, メイリオ, Meiryo, Osaka, &quot;ＭＳ Ｐゴシック&quot;, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">6-3 The provisions of the preceding two paragraphs shall not apply if the Company has no obligation to correct or suspend use due to the Personal Information Protection Law or other laws and regulations.</p>
<h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Noto Sans USAese&quot;, &quot;ヒラギノ角ゴ Pro W3&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro&quot;, メイリオ, Meiryo, Osaka, &quot;ＭＳ Ｐゴシック&quot;, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, verdana, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 32px; color: rgb(25, 47, 96); margin: 40px 0px 15px; font-size: 26px; padding: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">7. Anonymously processed information</h3>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(25, 47, 96); font-family: &quot;Noto Sans USAese&quot;, &quot;ヒラギノ角ゴ Pro W3&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro&quot;, メイリオ, Meiryo, Osaka, &quot;ＭＳ Ｐゴシック&quot;, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">7-1 The Company shall use anonymously processed information (meaning the information specified in Article 2, Paragraph 9 of the Personal Information Protection Act, and configuring the anonymously processed information database, etc. specified in Article 2, Paragraph 10 of the Act). The same shall apply hereinafter) when processing personal information in accordance with the standards set forth in the rules of the Personal Information Protection Commission.</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(25, 47, 96); font-family: &quot;Noto Sans USAese&quot;, &quot;ヒラギノ角ゴ Pro W3&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro&quot;, メイリオ, Meiryo, Osaka, &quot;ＭＳ Ｐゴシック&quot;, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">7-2 When we create anonymously processed information, we will take measures for security management in accordance with the standards set forth in the rules of the Personal Information Protection Commission.</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(25, 47, 96); font-family: &quot;Noto Sans USAese&quot;, &quot;ヒラギノ角ゴ Pro W3&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro&quot;, メイリオ, Meiryo, Osaka, &quot;ＭＳ Ｐゴシック&quot;, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">7-3 When the Company has created anonymously processed information, the Company shall publish the items of personal information included in the anonymously processed information as provided for in the rules of the Personal Information Protection Committee.</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(25, 47, 96); font-family: &quot;Noto Sans USAese&quot;, &quot;ヒラギノ角ゴ Pro W3&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro&quot;, メイリオ, Meiryo, Osaka, &quot;ＭＳ Ｐゴシック&quot;, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">7-4 When providing anonymously processed information (including information created by the Company and provided by a third party; the same shall apply hereinafter unless otherwise specified) to the third party In accordance with the rules of the Personal Information Protection Commission, the items of personal information included in anonymously processed information provided to a third party and the method of providing the information are disclosed in advance, and Specify that the information pertaining to the provision is anonymously processed information.</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(25, 47, 96); font-family: &quot;Noto Sans USAese&quot;, &quot;ヒラギノ角ゴ Pro W3&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro&quot;, メイリオ, Meiryo, Osaka, &quot;ＭＳ Ｐゴシック&quot;, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">7-5 In handling the anonymously processed information, the Company shall (1) collate the anonymously processed information with other information to identify the user associated with the personal information used to create the anonymously processed information; and (2) Acquiring a description deleted from the personal information or a personal identification code or information on the processing method performed in accordance with the provisions of Article 36, Paragraph 1 of the Personal Information Protection Act ((2) is a third party Only for such anonymously processed information provided by the Company).</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(25, 47, 96); font-family: &quot;Noto Sans USAese&quot;, &quot;ヒラギノ角ゴ Pro W3&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro&quot;, メイリオ, Meiryo, Osaka, &quot;ＭＳ Ｐゴシック&quot;, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">7-6 The Company shall take necessary and appropriate measures for the security management of anonymously processed information, handle complaints regarding the creation and other handling of anonymously processed information, and other measures necessary to ensure the proper handling of anonymously processed information And make efforts to publish the details of such measures.</p>
<h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Noto Sans USAese&quot;, &quot;ヒラギノ角ゴ Pro W3&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro&quot;, メイリオ, Meiryo, Osaka, &quot;ＭＳ Ｐゴシック&quot;, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, verdana, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 32px; color: rgb(25, 47, 96); margin: 40px 0px 15px; font-size: 26px; padding: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">8. Inquiries</h3>
